name: Sometimes I lose control
description:
And then the going gets rough.

I've always kind of felt like a fisherman on a boat, being tossed around by the waves, a little helpless but optimistic that I'm not steering into the storm but to the shore.

I may lose some of my cargo, step on a rusty nail that I didn't take care of, heck even if my ship is being torn to pieces... somehow I'll get through this.
